    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Syncing an ethereum node is **disk io** intensive. It can only ever sync to an SSD even now, adding swap will just further increase disk IO insanely. Please don't ever add swap to a machine tbh, it just doesn't make sense, it won't crash an app, but runtime will be insanely slow.\r\n\r\nAre you doing a fast sync or a full sync by any chance? SSD or HDD?",
